headline.main: CAIRO PREMIER CONFIDENT; Quotes Eden Message Respecting Resolve to Defend Egypt

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, June 30 (UP) -Premier Mustapha Nahas Pasha told Parliament today that he had received a message from British Foreign Secretary Anthony Eden reiterating that Britain not only was resolved to defend Egyptian territory, but had available ways and means of doing so.
abstract: Egyptian Premier Nahas Pasha quotes Sec Eden message on Brit resolve to defend Egypt Parliament
